snippet.title: Northgard - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Northgard, the revolutionary Strategy Game is finally coming to Nintendo Switch! Build your settlement, gather resources, survive harsh winters and defeat your enemies in this million seller hit!

Learn more about the game: http://northgard.net
Learn more about us: http://shirogames.com

Follow Shiro Games on:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/northgard
Twitter: https://twitter.com/shirogames 

#NintendoSwitch #Northgard
